This is the second and general reply answerin'g to the general >interrogation in v. 35-ζ who shall separate us' from the love of Christ ‘?' To that question an answer is here returned, and the sub- stance of it is—-‘ no created thing shall separate us from the love of God in Christ.' In these two verses the reply is first proved, and then variously amplified.
